    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\">\n<p>You unleash a virulent disease on a creature that you can see within range. The target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, it takes <span class=\"roller render-roller\" title=\"Click to roll. SHIFT to roll a critical hit, CTRL to half damage (rounding down).\" data-packed-dice=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;dice&quot;,&quot;rollable&quot;:true,&quot;toRoll&quot;:&quot;14d6&quot;,&quot;subType&quot;:&quot;damage&quot;}\">14d6</span> necrotic damage, or half as much damage on a successful save. The damage can't reduce the target's hit points below 1. If the target fails the saving throw, its hit point maximum is reduced for 1 hour by an amount equal to the necrotic damage it took. Any effect that removes a disease allows a creature's hit point maximum to return to normal before that time passes.</p>\n</div>",
